import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedUndiscriminatedUnionWithResponseProperty

client = AsyncSeedUndiscriminatedUnionWithResponseProperty(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.get_union()


asyncio.run(main())
